#LegendOfBhagatSingh 

Posted @withregram • @nishchaygogia Meri Dulhan Toh Azadi Hain...

The Warden of Lahore Central Jail Charat Singh dragged himself back to his room and burst into tears. In his thirty years of service he had witnessed many executions but never had he seen anyone mount the gallows as courageously as Bhagat Singh & his two comrades. The lives of three of the nation's finest and bravest young men had been brutally cut short by the British imperialists.

It was sacrifice on the altar of independence !

Shaheed Diwas
23rd March, 1931. 

Bhagat Singh was 23years old
Sukhdev Thapar was 23years old
Shivaram Rajguru was 22years old

- Nishchay
